Summary: Bright light moving in sky that was NOT a plan or star, but ..
divs: Sighting DetailsI watched in awe as a bright light traveled across the sky, it was the brightest thing next to the moon, it was silent, it was fast, it didn't blink it traveled approximately West North West to East South East, I said to my 3 year old son, "Wow do you see that UFO ?" and he said, "Dad, Come-on man, really ? You that stupid ? That's just the International Space Station".
